{"version":3,"term":{"cols":90,"rows":24},"timestamp":1783409182,"command":"studio recording=getting-started step=session","title":"Getting Started With OmegaFlow"}
[0.356, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Install the OmegaFlow CLI.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.256, "o", "Successfully installed omegaflow\r\n"]
[0.023, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.038, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Create a tiny but complete recording.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.257, "o", "Wrote /tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/config.yaml\r\nWrote /tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/hello/omegaflow.md\r\nWrote /tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/hello/scripts/hello.sh\r\nWrote /tmp/omegaflow-hello/docs/hello.md\r\n"]
[0.211, "o", "/tmp/omegaflow-hello/docs/hello.md\r\n/tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/config.yaml\r\n/tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/hello/omegaflow.md\r\n/tmp/omegaflow-hello/recordings/hello/scripts/hello.sh\r\n"]
[0.221, "o", "---\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "id: hello\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "title: Hello Video\r\noutputs:\r\n  cast: site/videos/hello.cast\r\npublish:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  default: docs\r\n  build_surfaces:\r\n  - docs\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  - html\r\n  surfaces:"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    docs:\r\n      type: docusaurus_mdx\r\n      file: docs/hello.md\r\n      placeholder: hello-video\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      component: VideoPlayer\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    html:\r\n      type: standalone_html\r\n      file: site/videos/hello.html\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "---\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "# Hello Video\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "This Markdown file is the source for one generated terminal video.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nThe YAML header names the recording, chooses output paths, and declares where\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "the finished video can be published. The prose explains the walkthrough for\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "readers and future maintainers. The fenced `studio-directive` blocks tell\r\nOmegaFlow what to record.\r\n\r\n```yaml studio-directive\r\nscene: Hello Video\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe scene is the title shown by the player. Beats are the steps in the video.\r\nThis beat runs a small shell script kept in this video's `scripts/` directory.\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "```yaml studio-directive\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "beat:\r\n  id: hello\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  heading: Say Hello\r\n  narration: Run the support script and verify the terminal output.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  caption: A one-command terminal recording.\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  actions:\r\n  - commands:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    - run_file: scripts/hello.sh\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      display: bash scripts/hello.sh\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "      expect:\r\n        output_contains:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "        - hello from OmegaFlow\r\n```\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\nPublish surfaces in the header let the same recording update docs or write a\r\nstandalone HTML page.\r\n"]
[0.029, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.035, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m# Build the tiny video from the script.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[1.839, "o", "pass wrote recording: site/videos/hello.cast\r\npass wrote retimed cast: site/videos/hello.retimed.cast\r\npass wrote publish surface: docs/hello.md\r\npass wrote publish surface: site/videos/hello.html\r\n"]
[0.025, "o", "\r\n"]
